+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |      Desired Perf  ---->|                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
+                     |                       |                         |                       |
